    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant wear, including large dents, deep scratches, and noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches and undercarriage. Mechanically, the car requires major repairs; the engine has a persistent knock, the transmission slips in higher gears, and the brakes are near the end of their life. The interior is also heavily worn with torn seats and a broken infotainment system, making this a suitable choice only for someone looking for a serious restoration project or a parts donor.",
