      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a refined interior, it balances sophisticated performance with proven reliability. Every aspect of this automobile has been vetted to ensure it meets our standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. A distinguished choice for those seeking an exceptional driving experience and lasting value.",
      "price": 36850.0,
